				(color 132 132 132 1)
			)
		)
		(uuid "64935ffb-e266-474d-84e0-45308d1aa325")
	)
	(text "*NOTE: this means we cannot amplify this first stage more than 2.5.\nwe should set around 2.0-2.3 to maximize amplification potential\nfor smaller signals without risking saturation of the amp."
